{"id":"tawassul","ar_title":"دعاء التوسل","en_title":"Dua al-Tawassul","count":169,"verses":[{"n":1,"ar":"اَللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ وَأَتَوَجَّهُ إِلَيْكَ","en":"O Allah, I beseech You and turn my face toward You"},{"n":2,"ar":"بِنَبِيِّكَ نَبِيِّ ٱلرَّحْمَةِ","en":"in the name of Your Prophet; the Prophet of Mercy,"},{"n":3,"ar":"مُحَمَّدٍ صَلَّىٰ ٱللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَآلِهِ","en":"Muhammad—may Allah send blessings to him and his Household."},{"n":4,"ar":"يَا أَبَا ٱلْقَاسِمِ","en":"ya aba alqasimi"},{"n":5,"ar":"يَا رَسُولَ ٱللَّهِ","en":"ya rasula allahi"},{"n":6,"ar":"يَا إِمَامَ ٱلرَّحْمَةِ","en":"O Chief of Mercy!"},{"n":7,"ar":"يَا سَيِّدَنَا وَمَوْلاَنَا","en":"O our master and chief!"},{"n":8,"ar":"إِنَّا تَوَجَّهْنَا وَٱسْتَشْفَعْنَا","en":"We are turning our faces toward you, seeking your intercession"},{"n":9,"ar":"وَتَوَسَّلْنَا بِكَ إِلَىٰ ٱللَّهِ","en":"and your advocacy for us before Allah;"},{"n":10,"ar":"وَقَدَّمْنَاكَ بَيْنَ يَدَيْ حَاجَاتِنَا","en":"and we are presenting you [as our intermediary] for the settlement of our needs."},{"n":11,"ar":"يَا وَجِيهاً عِنْدَ ٱللَّهِ","en":"O well-esteemed with Allah,"},{"n":12,"ar":"إِشْفَعْ لَنَا عِنْدَ ٱللَّهِ","en":"intercede for us before Allah."},{"n":13,"ar":"يَا أَبَا ٱلْحَسَنِ","en":"ya aba alhasani"},{"n":14,"ar":"يَا أَمِيرَ ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","en":"O commander of the Believers!"},{"n":15,"ar":"يَا عَلِيُّ بْنَ أَبِي طَالِبٍ","en":"O `Ali, son of Abu-Talib!"},{"n":16,"ar":"يَا حُجَّةَ ٱللَّهِ عَلَىٰ خَلْقِهِ","en":"O Allah’s Argument against His creatures!"},{"n":17,"ar":"يَا سَيِّدَنَا وَمَوْلاَنَا","en":"O our master and chief!"},{"n":18,"ar":"إِنَّا تَوَجَّهْنَا وَٱسْتَشْفَعْنَا","en":"We are turning our faces toward you, seeking your intercession"},{"n":19,"ar":"وَتَوَسَّلْنَا بِكَ إِلَىٰ اللّهِ","en":"and your advocacy for us before Allah;"},{"n":20,"ar":"وَقَدَّمْنَاكَ بَيْنَ يَدَيْ حَاجَاتِنَا","en":"and we are presenting you [as our intermediary] for the settlement of our needs."},{"n":21,"a