Hasan the son of `Ali!"},{"n":133,"ar":"أَيُّهَا ٱلزَّكِيُّ ٱلْعَسْكَرِيُّ","en":"O immaculate resident of `Askar [city]!"},{"n":134,"ar":"يَا بْنَ رَسُولِ ٱللَّهِ","en":"O son of Allah’s Messenger!"},{"n":135,"ar":"يَا حُجَّةَ ٱللَّهِ عَلَىٰ خَلْقِهِ","en":"O Allah’s Argument against His creatures!"},{"n":136,"ar":"يَا سَيِّدَنَا وَمَوْلاَنَا","en":"O our master and chief!"},{"n":137,"ar":"إِنَّا تَوَجَّهْنَا وَٱسْتشْفَعْنَا","en":"we are turning our faces toward you, seeking your intercession"},{"n":138,"ar":"وَتَوَسَّلْنَا بِكَ إِلَىٰ ٱللَّهِ","en":"and your advocacy for us before Allah;"},{"n":139,"ar":"وَقَدَّمْنَاكَ بَيْنَ يَدَيْ حَاجَاتِنَا","en":"and we are presenting you [as our intermediary] for the settlement of our needs."},{"n":140,"ar":"يَا وَجِيهاً عِنْدَ ٱللَّهِ","en":"O well-esteemed with Allah,"},{"n":141,"ar":"إِشْفَعْ لَنَا عِنْدَ ٱللَّهِ","en":"intercede for us before Allah."},{"n":142,"ar":"يَا وَصِيَّ ٱلْحَسَنِ","en":"O successor of al-Hasan!"},{"n":143,"ar":"وَٱلْخَلَفُ ٱلْحُجَّةُ","en":"O descendant [of the Infallibles] and Argument [of Allah]!"},{"n":144,"ar":"أَيُّهَا ٱلْقَائِمُ ٱلْمُنْتَظَرُ ٱلْمَهْدِيُّ","en":"O Riser, Awaited, and Well-guided!"},{"n":145,"ar":"يَا بْنَ رَسُولِ ٱللَّهِ","en":"O son of Allah’s Messenger!"},{"n":146,"ar":"يَا حُجَّةَ ٱللَّهِ عَلَىٰ خَلْقِهِ","en":"O Allah’s Argument against His creatures!"},{"n":147,"ar":"يَا سَيِّدَنَا وَمَوْلاَنَا","en":"O our master and chief!"},{"n":148,"ar":"إِنَّا تَوَجَّهْنَا وَٱسْتَشْفَعْنَا","en":"we are turning our faces toward you, seeking your intercession"},{"n":149,"ar":"وَتَوَسَّلْنَا بِكَ إِلَىٰ ٱللَّهِ","en":"and your advocacy for us before Allah;"},{"n":150,"ar":"وَقَدَّمْنَاكَ بَيْنَ يَدَيْ حَاجَاتِنَا","en":"and we are presenting you [as our intermediary] for the settlement of our needs."},{"n":151,"ar":"يَا وَجِيهاً عِنْدَ ٱللَّهِ","en":"O well-esteemed with Allah,"},{"n":152,"ar":"إِشْفَعْ لَنَا عِنْدَ ٱللَّهِ","en":"intercede for us before Allah."},{"n":153,"ar":"يَا سَادَتِي وَمَوَالِيَّ","en":"O my chiefs and masters!"},{"n":154,"ar":"إِنِّي تَوَجَّهْتُ بِكُمْ","en":"I am turning my face toward Allah in the names of you [all],"},{"n":155,"ar":"ائِمَّتِي وَعُدَّتِي","en":"for you are my leaders and my supporters"},{"n":156,"ar":"لِيَوْمِ فَقْرِي وَحَاجَتِي","en":"on the day of my destitution and neediness"},{"n":157,"ar":"إِلَىٰ ٱللَّهِ","en":"ila allahi"},{"n":158,"ar":"وَتَوَسَّلْتُ بِكُمْ إِلَىٰ ٱللَّهِ","en":"I am seeking your advocacy for me before Allah"},{"n":159,"ar":"وَٱسْتَشْفَعْتُ بِكُمْ إِلَىٰ ٱللَّهِ","en":"and seeking your intercession for me before Allah;"},{"n":160,"ar":"فَٱشْفَعُوا لِي عِنْدَ ٱللَّهِ","en":"so, (please) intercede for me before Allah"},{"n":161,"ar":"وَٱسْتَنْقِذُونِي مِنْ ذُنُوبِي عِنْدَ ٱللَّهِ","en":"and save me from my sins before Allah,"},{"n":162,"ar":"فَإنَّكُمْ وَسيلَتِي إِلَىٰ ٱللَّهِ","en":"for you are my means to Allah"},{"n":163,"ar":"وَبِحُبِّكُمْ وَبِقُرْبِكُمْ ارْجُو نَجَاةً مِنَ ٱللَّهِ","en":"and through my love for you and my seeking nearness to you do I hope for salvation from Allah."},{"n":164,"ar":"فَكُونُوا عِنْدَ ٱللَّهِ رَجَائِي","en":"So, be my hope before Allah."},{"n":165,"ar":"يَا سَادَتِي يَا اوْلِيَاءَ ٱللَّهِ","en":"O my masters! O Allah’s intimate servants!"},{"n":166,"ar":"صَلَّىٰ ٱللَّهُ عَلَيْهِمْ اجْمَعينَ","en":"May Allah bless you all"},{"n":167,"ar":"وَلَعَنَ ٱللَّهُ اعْدَاءَ ٱللَّهِ ظَالِمِيهِمْ","en":"and may Allah curse the enemies of Allah; those who wronged you,"},{"n":168,"ar":"مِنَ ٱلاوَّلِينَ وَٱلآخِرِينَ","en":"from the past and the last generations."},{"n":169,"ar":"آمِينَ رَبَّ ٱلْعَالَمينَ","en":"Respond to us, O Lord of the Worlds!"}]}